OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FScattered
OL,6,Fshowers fading, with some late
OL,7,Fsunshine and then clear periods
OL,8,Ffollowing. Cloud amounts should
OL,9,Fincrease from the east later in the
OL,10,Fnight, bringing the odd spot of light
OL,11,Frain or drizzle in places. Chilly,
OL,12,Fwith local grass frost.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTuesday:FEarly cloud largely clearing
OL,15,Fwestwards to leave a mainly fine day
OL,16,Fwith sunny spells. Temperatures near-
OL,17,Fnormal, tempered by the strengthening
OL,18,Feasterly breeze, especially in coastal
OL,19,Fdistricts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
